    "causal_summary": "Documentation and OpenCode-component authoring parent hub. One advisor identity that routes through mode-registry.json + hub-router.json to nine nested workflow packets (create-skill/-parent, create-readme, create-agent, create-command, create-feature-catalog, create-manual-testing-playbook, create-benchmark, create-flowchart, create-quality-control). The universal create-quality-control pipeline lives once in shared/ and is consumed by every packet. It matters because it gives the workspace one discoverable identity for authoring and validating high-quality documentation and components, with per-artifact workflows isolated in self-contained packets.",
